{"tid":1767984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美商務部長指香港局勢在美中貿易協議中是一個變數","createTime":"2019-12-03T17:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T17:50:43.000Z","uid":125193,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8568a43a2f4b637248d0c72250ceee9faa151c4b","tid":1767984,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:15:20.000Z","msg":"<strong>美國商務部長羅斯說，香港局勢在美國與中國的貿易協議中是一個變數</strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">又形容中國暫停審批美軍艦機，到香港休假申請的反制措施，不是甚麼大事。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n羅斯說，總統特朗普已明確表示，在完成與中國的貿易協議方面，在時間上沒有壓力，又強調特朗普對達成協議的目標，沒有改變。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495831-20191204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495831-20191204.htm&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=83e99222\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495831-20191204.htm&h=9f94c47a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495831-20191204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f9c2739f6c56ae3b0519e2fca66fcf7c2cab1391","tid":1767984,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2761423dc9aae47db157b7fb954d81f40726ea80","tid":1767984,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6937591d627a8aedb738b373106ddc84680102dd","tid":1767984,"uid":144522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"292969c85ca091c7d69b38e061c0f64d8218c051","tid":1767984,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\